t\": \"Tabuteau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Tabuteau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Tabuteau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TottenhamdefenderCristian Romerohas expressed a desire to play forArgentinaat theOlympicsthis summer.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's football at theParis Games runs from July 24 to August 10and finishes the week before the new Premier League season starts.\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 657, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999999529336, \"rank\": 4.6307601353537075e-11, \"text\": \"Premier League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is an Under-23s tournament but each country is allowed to select three older players.\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 697, \"end\": 706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reserve_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999962788024, \"rank\": 3.5662938626727735e-09, \"text\": \"Under-23s\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reserve_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reserve_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Romero will already be representing Argentina at the Copa America this summer - which runs between June 20 and July 14 - but has made himself available for the selection for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\", \"score\": 0.7694523531450086, \"rank\": 0.1288217668555633, \"text\": \"Romero\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\"}, {\"begin\": 814, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6681053196294864, \"rank\": 0.4967570210966158, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never had the chance to be in the Olympic Games and I would love to,\\\" said Romero.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1045, \"end\": 1051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\", \"score\": 0.7694523531450086, \"rank\": 0.1288217668555633, \"text\": \"Romero\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, it does not depend on me, but if you want to take me I am available for the Argentine national team.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999773379800816, \"rank\": 2.2661545422228956e-05, \"text\": \"Argentine national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I continue with the same enthusiasm and desire as always to continue doing things well at the club to continue having the possibility of being here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clubs can veto call-ups, as the Olympics is not recognised by FIFA, andSpursare unlikely to be happy about the prospect of Romero playing in two major tournaments this summer.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9996454462193507, \"rank\": 0.000354668336756022, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, {\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\", \"score\": 0.7694523531450086, \"rank\": 0.1288217668555633, \"text\": \"Romero\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they could be left in a difficult position if the centre-back is called up for the Olympics and expresses a desire to play in Paris.\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1627, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997950221978, \"rank\": 2.0497786162842793e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Losing Romero so close to the season would not be ideal, while there is also a risk of injury and the prospect of him needing time off afterwards and missing the start of the season.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\", \"score\": 0.7694523531450086, \"rank\": 0.1288217668555633, \"text\": \"Romero\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths tol